Name: Average resolution time for 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'

Name: Total time spent in 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Average time between 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and 'Request Payment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Time difference between the earliest and latest 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' for re-submissions
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Minimum time to resolve a case after 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Maximum time a case remains in 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' before moving to the next activity
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x00000221C2305210> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total time cases spend in 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' compared to 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Difference in average case duration between cases with and without 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING does not occur

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to the end of the process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Total elapsed time for cases involving 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' across different budget numbers (grouped by 'case:BudgetNumber')
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and the end of case grouped by the last value of case:BudgetNumber

Name: 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' cycle time as a proportion of total process time
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case
